name: hic et squigl #1627
description:
the squigl tetris 3. 

controls: left arrow - move left. right arrow - move right. down arrow - move down. up arrow - rotate piece. space - fast down. esc - end game. p - pause.

mobile controls appear on mobile full screen view.
double tap the down button to fast down.

hic et squigl tokens flow through hic et nunc galleries.
